Package com.semedy.reasoner.parser.oologic

Class OOLogicColorListener

java.lang.Object
com.semedy.reasoner.parser.oologic.OOLogicColorListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
OOLogicGrammarListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class OOLogicColorListener extends Object implements OOLogicGrammarListener
This class provides an empty implementation of OOLogicGrammarListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
